Synopsis:           Base64 implementation for String's.
Description:
    This Base64 implementation uses the characters
        A-Z a-z 0-9 + /
    along with
        =
    to signal the number of characters mod 3.
    It is compliant with both PEM (RFC 989 / RFC 1421) and MIME (RFC 2045).
